long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
"IIIKCOM SEARCH ENGINE" Chrome extension enables the user's to have current time with animated background on new tab.  The background image are taken from pexels.com. 

By clicking "Add to Chrome", I accept and agree to install the "IIIKCOM SEARCH ENGINE " Chrome extension and set Chrome™️ New Tab search to that provided by the service and the Terms of Use and Privacy Policy. The extension will update your search settings and will change your New Tab search services provided by Microsoft Bing.
